title: How to Stop Being Lazy & Be More Productive
itunes:title: How to Stop Being Lazy & Be More Productive
description:
In order to create the life you want, you are going to have to destroy your laziness and become more productive. In this episode, I am going to teach you some simple strategies that I teach my highest paying clients to conquer their laziness and increase their productivity.

Follow me on IG here: https://instagram.com/robdialjr
